            <title>[FLINK-8808] Enable RestClusterClient to submit jobs to local Dispatchers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-8808</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;RestClusterClient&lt;/tt&gt; should be able to submit a job to a &lt;tt&gt;Dispatcher&lt;/tt&gt; which runs in a local &lt;tt&gt;ActorSystem&lt;/tt&gt; on the same host as the &lt;tt&gt;RestClusterClient&lt;/tt&gt;. This is the case for test cases.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
