&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    The RestClusterClient resolves a dispatcher address without an explicit host&lt;br/&gt;
    to &apos;localhost&apos;. That way we allow the RestClusterClient to talk to a Dispatcher&lt;br/&gt;
    which runs in a local ActorSystem.&lt;/p&gt;

